what_worked: Applied single_pass_aggregation, prefetch_fact_join, multi_dimension_prefetch: Consolidated duplicate store_sales scans into single-pass CTEs, pre-computed both rankings simultaneously, and staged joins to minimize table scans.
why_it_worked: Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
